      "description": "In teamfights, start by hitting a marked enemy hero with Arlott's 2nd Skill, then get into position to unleash his Ultimate on the enemy team to CC and mark them. Use Arlott's 2nd Skill to cut through the enemy from target to target. When all marks have been used up, use his 1st Skill to CC and mark enemies again, and continue to chain his 2nd Skill."
